00:04:29.508 --> 00:04:30.718
BORRAR

00:04:38.138 --> 00:04:39.348
Reportero Lee.

00:04:39.938 --> 00:04:42.758
Un percance más como este,

00:04:42.808 --> 00:04:44.838
